# Nested Iframes communication example

Prerequisites: node.js

1. Install dependencies

`npm install`

2. Run server

`npm run start`

It starts http 3 live-server Webservers on ports 8180, 8181, 8182.

3. Browse to http://127.0.0.1:8180
